      }}>{`Gitter`}</a>{` chatroom if you need to talk to us at any time regarding technical issues, feature ideas, or anything else you would like to share with the OpenCRVS community. If you would like to reach out to our management team, complete our online contact form at `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://www.opencrvs.org/"
      }}>{`opencrvs.org`}</a></p>
