    <p><em parentName="p">{`We take every action possible to ensure that no-one is left behind. We are inclusive, don't discriminate and protect as a priority.`}</em></p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "we-are-human-centered"
    }}>{`We are human-centered`}</h2>
    <p><em parentName="p">{`We put people first.`}</em>{` `}<em parentName="p">{`We design with our users to ensure that the system works for them.`}</em></p>
